# Publish only the sanitized GitHub Pages site by default.
*

!.gitignore
!site/
!site/**
!.github/
!.github/workflows/
!.github/workflows/pages.yml

# Keep local/macOS noise out even if ignore rules change later.
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store

# Never publish source CV material or generated resume artifacts from this workspace.
*.docx
*.pdf
*.md
rendered_profile*/
rendered_tegh_profile*/
roger_cv/
tools/
